Hi friends it s been a while but we are back with awesome premium features called 365 me Plus . Missed a question Use Jokers to unlock it and save your streak Lock your diary make sure authentication is enabled on your phone for this feature . For those who want to stay in the free version: Rest assured today s question will always be available for free. We would appreciate your support. Have fun with the app!

Thank you for your great feedback. Your wish is our command: To help you to stay focused on today s question future questions are now hidden.

Save your streak! Questions that are open have a red label so you won t miss out on any question. We solved a problem when launching the app on the iPad in landscape mode. However we recommend to use the app in portrait mode for better user experience.
Sharing is caring! Help you friends to reflect about their lives by sharing interesting questions with them.
Many of you asked for it and now it s here: you can create a backup of your answers. When you re install the app for example you can directly import your saved answers again.
In case you did not know: Questions answered this year will be asked again next year so you can see you personal growth.
Hey there! If you are missing out on some questions: set up your reminders in the setting. We have cleaned up our code to make sure everything works fine for you.
